{"tid":1507382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"容祖兒蜜會王菀之已婚叔仔 戴口罩帽子遮樣冚新戀情","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:14:59.000Z","uid":307551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67c89fab83542c8f2e0f719abd8ad4910ca0e83b","tid":1507382,"uid":307551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190826/59931078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F59931078&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=7be72645\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190826%2F59931078&h=11b5751c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190826/59931078</a><br />\n<br />\n39歲容祖兒於今年初正式認跟劉浩龍分手，回復單身的她聲稱未有新戀情，早前與楊政龍的緋聞只是得啖笑，而劉浩龍又忽然網晒車牌「MY JOEY」的車相，疑似對祖兒未忘情，不過，據知祖兒冇打算食回頭草，有知情人士向《蘋果》爆料，指祖兒秘撻已為人夫的王菀之叔仔Gavin So，《蘋果》連月追蹤，發現兩人約會時刻意低調，祖兒必戴口罩和帽子遮掩，「蘇兒戀」終於斷正。<br />\n貌似梁競徽的Gavin任職連鎖食店高層，根據線報，兩人於7月11日出發蜜遊東京4日3夜，14號返港當日，《蘋果》果然在機場拍到兩人前後腳出閘，為免戀情外洩的祖兒，由出發到返港都是單拖行動，神不知鬼不覺；返港翌日（15日）兩人急不及待又約見面，早上10時許返工的Gavin，晚上7時許收工後，在公司樓下扯完支煙，即急步搭港鐵去中環，其間不停撳手機。<br />\n到達中環後，Gavin先去食店買了外賣，然後站在街上等人，不久後祖兒的保母車到達，惟祖兒並沒有第一時間落車，Gavin亦相當有警覺性，左望右望視察了約20秒，之後祖兒才匆匆落車，戴口罩和漁夫帽遮樣的她，急步跟Gavin走入一棟商業大廈，而祖兒的司機就充當保鑣，不停在街上行來行去，查看有否傳媒在場偷拍。<br />\n直至3個多小時後，夜深人靜兩人才齊齊落樓，祖兒由步出大廈到上車前都周圍望，十分謹慎，她的七人車就泊正在門外，方便兩人只需行幾步就上車，跟在身後的Gavin不停打呵欠，一面倦容，上車前亦四圍望清楚環境，最後兩人同車離去。<br />\n其後祖兒要忙於為演唱會綵排，沒有時間約會談戀愛，直至18場紅館騷開鑼，Gavin幾乎晚晚都到紅館報到，陪不同朋友去睇騷，似足半個男主人，不過Gavin表現好低調，有時到後台攞工作證入場，有時就持門票入場，事關後台耳目眾多，以免被人發現晚晚現身，令「蘇兒戀」曝光。<br />\n《蘋果》今日致電Gavin，問他是否與祖兒拍拖，Gavin說：「啊唔係㗎唔好意思，唔該你。」跟祖兒是甚麼關係？Gavin未有回應，再問他與太太是否離婚，Gavin說：「我冇嘢講呀，唔該你。」說罷即掛上電話。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64df877b7becaeb26625cb8751ea113affcbd006","tid":1507382,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=b1cd1a9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"46fd2ee2ef8a85f5b5f24e27148ed94266ab834c","tid":1507382,"uid":22700,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"雞容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2646d168c03212a8d8b9566165ca22e3769587","tid":1507382,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"(外國文宣) 大家係咪miss 左一粒核彈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"177ed83f8afa30b67ca7e33e5ccd89689b7b5b0a","tid":1507382,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"關我鬼事"},{"pid":"dcf3d5277dcd8600c77d19d74190262bb9b84987","tid":1507382,"uid":258513,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"容祖兒都啱咁重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b4e5aacebe50f193e0b07f1d8ebac4b9f1078b","tid":1507382,"uid":52697,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雞容都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞容搞人老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa4bd5cd9d6964fd6dab3c209bd677ef5405801","tid":1507382,"uid":62481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"做咩同唯唯一齊"},{"pid":"ae611db69dd9b28c3a156d5410e73f787a867ab9","tid":1507382,"uid":82018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"帶哂口罩 如果被黑警查身分證都幾好笑"},{"pid":"3abd6738c82a92fdab27cdb71d9e575f19d497e5","tid":1507382,"uid":21103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae611db69dd9b28c3a156d5410e73f787a867ab9","tid":1507382,"uid":82018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"帶哂口罩 如果被黑警查身分證都幾好笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}